<HEADLINE>
<P>
DEATH OF WRITER EDWARD ABBEY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
It was with great sadness that I learned of the death of author Edward Abbey. I 
will not be able to think of the arid beauty of northern Arizona or Utah's 
Canyonlands without his writings coming to mind. 
</P>
<P>
I hope that his publishers will release the draft of his last novel. A sequel 
to "The Monkey Wrench Gang" will be welcomed with open arms. 
