<P>
Photo, Eric Latzky, from left, Frederique Delacoste, Paul Monette and Mallory 
Tarcher Dougherty attend an awards ceremony honoring writers who have explored 
the subject of AIDS. TAMMY LECHNER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
