<P>
Three more shows have been added for Neil Diamond's upcoming stand at the 
Forum. With the first three concerts (June 28-30) having sold out within three 
hours, additional shows were added for July 5-7, and there may be more to come. 
In 1983, Diamond's seven-night stay at the Forum sold-out just as quickly. 
