<HEADLINE>
<P>
PEREZ DEFENDS TITLE IN IRVINE FIGHT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Tommy Perez of Santa Ana will defend his California super welterweight title 
tonight against Ryan Hammond of Vallejo in a 12-round fight at the Irvine 
Marriott. 
</P>
<P>
Perez has a 20-3 record. Hammond is 16-2. 
</P>
<P>
The first bout in the five-fight card begins at 7 p.m. 
</P>
</TEXT>
