through South Pasadena? Then everyone would be happy! 
</P>
<P>
If the light-rail project can tunnel under Wilshire Boulevard in Los Angeles, 
why can't we go ahead with the same idea under South Pasadena? 
</P>
<P>
C. L. SWANSON 
